es-new-single-people-watching-and-teases-album-news-3810920">备受期待的第三张专辑“People Watching”，</a>该专辑将于 2 月 21 日通过 Polydor 分享（<a href="https://samfender.lnk.to/peoplewatching" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。</p><p>这张唱片由 Fender 与他的乐队成员 Dean Thompson 和 Joe Atkinson、制作人 Markus Dravs 以及<a href="https://nme-next.netlify.app/artists/the-war-on-drugs">The War On Drugs</a>的 Adam Granduciel 共同制作。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-music-with-the-war-on-drugs-adam-granduciel-3601247">首先暗示，早在 2024 年 3 月，他就一直在与后者合作</a>，与制作人、工程师和其他音乐家一起分享他们在录音室里的镜头。然后，十月 Fender 确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-teases-new-album-is-finished-and-mastered-3799886">新专辑已经完成并“掌握”</a> 。这将是他自 2021 年第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">《Seventeen Going Under》</a>以来的第一张 LP。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEhnuKVzNMs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https